    "(2) Supporting educational purposes by identifying appropriate cases for case-centered study.",
    "(3) Facilitating interactive queries related to PET reading for clinicians, based on a database of past reports.",
    "This proof-of-concept study seeks to demonstrate the feasibility and benefits of integrating advanced LLM capabilities with a vast repository of PET imaging data, aiming to set enhanced medical imaging reporting practices.",
